01:34:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/inside-the-quest-to-make-a-safer-football-helmet</guid></item><item><title>状态表征和价值的中皮质纹状体强化学习对精神分裂症机制的影响</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/mesocorticostriatal-reinforcement-learning-of-state-representation-and-value-with-implications-for-the-mechanisms-of-schizophrenia</link><description>中皮质纹状体多巴胺投射对于价值学习、动机控制和认知功能至关重要。然而，虽然多巴胺在价值学习中作为奖励预测错误（RPE）的作用已被广泛了解，但在动机控制和认知功能中的确切作用仍然更加难以捉摸。从计算角度来看，这对应于虽然中纹状体多巴胺的运作可以通过具有一维奖励/RPE和固定状态表示的简单强化学习（RL）模型进行最低程度的描述，但如何通过异质多巴胺反应实现特定奖励的动机控制，以及如何通过中皮质多巴胺形成复杂的皮质状态表示，这些简单的模型无法捕获。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/mesocorticostriatal-reinforcement-learning-of-state-representation-and-value-with-implications-for-the-mechanisms-of-schizophrenia.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 May 2026 01:19:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/mesocorticostriatal-reinforcement-learning-of-state-representation-and-value-with-implications-for-the-mechanisms-of-schizophrenia</guid></item><item><title>火星真菌可以使红色星球的风化层变得肥沃，适合农作物生长</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/mars-fungi-could-make-red-planet-regolith-fertile-for-crops</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 May 2026 01:04:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/mars-fungi-could-make-red-planet-regolith-fertile-for-crops</guid></item><item><title>外星机器人都在哪里？冯·诺依曼探测器的令人不寒而栗的想法</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/where-are-all-the-alien-robots-the-chilling-idea-of-von-neumann-probes</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 May 2026 00:49:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/where-are-all-the-alien-robots-the-chilling-idea-of-von-neumann-probes</guid></item><item><title>计算是新资本：人工智能代币如何成为硅谷最强大的货币</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/compute-is-the-new-capital-how-ai-tokens-became-the-valleys-most-powerful-currency</link><description>如果你想知道科技界现在真正看重什么，只需看看它正在衡量什么。我们曾经痴迷于代码行，然后一切都与每日活跃用户和参与度指标有关。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/compute-is-the-new-capital-how-ai-tokens-became-the-valleys-most-powerful-currency.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 May 2026 00:34:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/compute-is-the-new-capital-how-ai-tokens-became-the-valleys-most-powerful-currency</guid></item><item><title>科学家为机器人构建了可自我延续的合成大脑</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/scientists-built-synthetic-self-perpetuating-brain-for-robots</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 May 2026 00:19:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/scientists-built-synthetic-self-perpetuating-brain-for-robots</guid></item><item><title>脑细胞主宰毁灭：皮质实验室的生物计算机达到人工智能的重大里程碑</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/brain-cells-master-doom-cortical-labs-biological-computer-reaches-major-ai-milestone</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 May 2026 00:04:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/brain-cells-master-doom-cortical-labs-biological-computer-reaches-major-ai-milestone</guid></item><item><title>终纹脑啡肽神经元的床核有助于消耗诱导的盐食欲</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/bed-nucleus-of-stria-terminalis-enkephalin-neurons-contribute-to-depletion-induced-salt-appetite</link><description>钠的过度消耗会导致一系列有害的健康状况。因此，有必要更好地了解驱动钠食欲的神经机制。在这里，我们结合神经解剖学、转基因、行为和化学遗传学方法来研究终纹床核 (BNST) 脑啡肽神经元 (BNSTENK) 在雄性和雌性 pENK-Cre 小鼠钠食欲中的作用。我们的结果表明，Gi 介导的 BNSTENK 神经元信号传导可调节钠消耗后的盐消耗，但在钠充足时不会影响味觉偏好。此外，Gi 介导的 BNSTENK 神经元信号传导对剥夺引起的食物或水摄入或焦虑样行为没有影响。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/bed-nucleus-of-stria-terminalis-enkephalin-neurons-contribute-to-depletion-induced-salt-appetite.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 May 2026 23:49:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/bed-nucleus-of-stria-terminalis-enkephalin-neurons-contribute-to-depletion-induced-salt-appetite</guid></item></channel></rss>